sections.heading: of State; Great Seal; custodian
sections.text: The Secretary of State shall safely keep and not suffer to be imitated or counterfeited the Great Seal of the State of Nebraska of the form and design prescribed by the Act approved June 15, 1867, as follows:SourceLaws 1867, ยง 1, p. 57;R.S.1913, ยง 5569;C.S.1922, ยง 487
